                                        Login to access the Advertising Tool.<br />
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="form-group mb-md">
                                        <div class="input-group input-group-icon">
                                            <label class="label label-control text-bold">Username</label>
                                            <input name="UserId" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter NT Username" required autocomplete="off" />
                                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                                <span class="icon icon-lg">
                                                    <svg class="lnr lnr-user"><use xlink:href="#lnr-user"></use></svg>
                                                </span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="form-group mb-md">
                                        <div class="input-group input-group-icon">
                                            <div class="col-sm-6 text-left p-none">
